---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Ariff Mohamed - Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer | MIT Cybersecurity Student"
  description="Expert Azure cloud solutions engineer specializing in security, automation, and compliance. Showcasing enterprise Azure projects including PowerShell automation, KQL analytics, storage security, and Intune device management."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="py-16 text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent-primary), var(--accent-secondary)); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="mb-4" style="font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: white; line-height: 1.2;">Ariff Mohamed</h1>
      <h2 class="mb-8" style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);">Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer | Security Specialist</h2>
      <p class="mb-8" style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; line-height: 1.6;">Transforming enterprise cloud infrastructure with security-first Azure architecture and innovative automation solutions. Currently advancing cybersecurity expertise at MIT.</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center" style="gap: 1rem;">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#projects">View Azure Projects</a>
        <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#about">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured Azure Projects -->
  <section class="py-16" id="projects">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-4" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);">Featured Azure Projects</h2>
      <p class="text-center mb-8" style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">Explore my specialized Azure implementations focused on automation, security, and enterprise management</p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="card-title">Azure Automation Hub</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-description mb-4">Comprehensive PowerShell runbook automation platform for enterprise user management, resource provisioning, and operational workflows. Features advanced scheduling, error handling, and audit trails.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://automation.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Explore Automation →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="card-title">Log Analytics Toolkit</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-description mb-4">Advanced KQL query library and monitoring dashboard suite for Azure security insights, performance analysis, and compliance reporting. Real-time alerting and custom workbooks included.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://log.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Explore Analytics →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="card-title">Secure Storage Patterns</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-description mb-4">Enterprise-grade Azure storage security implementations featuring encryption at rest and in transit, compliance frameworks, access policies, and data governance best practices.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://storage.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Explore Storage →</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="card-title">Device Compliance Monitor</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-description mb-4">Microsoft Intune-powered device management and compliance monitoring solution. Automated policy enforcement, security baselines, and comprehensive reporting for enterprise endpoints.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="https://compliance.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Explore Compliance →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Side Projects -->
  <section class="py-16" id="side-projects">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-4" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);">Side Projects</h2>
      <p class="text-center mb-8" style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">Personal development tools and experimental applications</p>
      
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <div class="card" style="max-width: 400px;">
          <div class="card-header">
            <h3 class="card-title">Todo Application</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-description mb-4">A modern, responsive task management application built with modern web technologies. Features task organization, priority management, and progress tracking.</p>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://todo.aglobaltec.com" target="_blank">Try Todo App →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Section -->
  <section class="py-16" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-8" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);">About Me</h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-2" style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; align-items: start;">
        <div>
          <p class="mb-4" style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">As an Azure Cloud Solutions Engineer specializing in security architecture, I bring deep technical expertise in enterprise cloud infrastructure, automation, and compliance. My experience spans large-scale Azure implementations, security frameworks, and innovative problem-solving for complex business challenges.</p>
          
          <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6;">Currently advancing my expertise through MIT's Cybersecurity program, I'm passionate about developing secure, scalable Azure solutions that drive business value while maintaining the highest security and compliance standards.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <h3 class="mb-4" style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent-primary);">Azure Specializations</h3>
          <div class="grid" style="gap: 0.5rem;">
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Azure Security Architecture
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              PowerShell Automation & Runbooks
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              KQL & Log Analytics
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Microsoft Intune Management
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Storage Security & Encryption
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Compliance & Governance
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Identity & Access Management
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              DevSecOps Implementation
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center" style="gap: 0.75rem; padding: 0.5rem 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <span style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;"></span>
              Threat Detection & Response
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact Section -->
  <section class="py-16" id="contact">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-4" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);">Get In Touch</h2>
      <p class="mb-8" style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 3rem;">Interested in collaborating on Azure cloud security solutions or discussing enterprise automation projects? Let's connect.</p>
      
      <div class="grid grid-3" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <a class="card text-center" href="mailto:ariff@aglobaltec.com" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: var(--transition);">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;">@</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Email</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-description">ariff@aglobaltec.com</p>
        </a>
        
        <a class="card text-center" href="https://linkedin.com/in/ariff" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: var(--transition);">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;">in</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">LinkedIn</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-description">Professional Profile</p>
        </a>
        
        <a class="card text-center" href="https://github.com/a-ariff" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: var(--transition);">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div style="width: 48px; height: 48px; background: var(--accent-primary); border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-weight: 600;"><></div>
            <h3 class="card-title">GitHub</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="card-description">Technical Portfolio</p>
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="mailto:ariff@aglobaltec.com">Start a Conversation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
